48:08.952 --> 48:10.087
Gosh.

48:12.990 --> 48:14.258
Rian's not in the audience either.

48:14.758 --> 48:15.626
What should we do?

48:16.627 --> 48:17.494
Ms. Ahn.

48:20.264 --> 48:22.833
May I go first?

48:26.270 --> 48:27.838
Do you want to do that?

48:29.072 --> 48:29.907
Yes.

48:44.721 --> 48:45.622
I'm sorry.

48:46.189 --> 48:47.858
Mind your manners.

48:47.925 --> 48:49.993
You can't climb over people
in the middle of a show.

48:50.060 --> 48:53.597
You shouldn't stick your legs
out like that.

48:53.964 --> 48:55.599
People need to pass by.

48:59.102 --> 49:00.837
Are you Rian's mother?

49:03.240 --> 49:05.309
Do you know me?

49:05.642 --> 49:06.843
Of course.

49:07.110 --> 49:10.113
Your picture is in the papers
for selling fake designer goods.

49:22.025 --> 49:24.761
It's Hae-seong, Dad!

49:28.165 --> 49:29.933
Sit down.

49:30.534 --> 49:32.069
She has to come in first place.

49:32.302 --> 49:33.437
Go, Hae-seong!

49:38.408 --> 49:40.177
When I felt lonely and things got tough,

49:41.311 --> 49:44.982
there was a friend
who gave me strength and comfort.

49:45.949 --> 49:46.783
Right now,

49:47.417 --> 49:51.221
that friend is feeling lonely
and having a hard time.

49:52.823 --> 49:54.791
Your duet partner isn't here yet?

49:59.396 --> 50:02.299
I think she'll be late.
I'll do it on my own.

50:02.699 --> 50:04.301
-Then you're on standby.
-Okay.

50:05.936 --> 50:06.870
But...

50:08.305 --> 50:13.243
my friend almost lost his dream
because of me.

50:16.613 --> 50:17.447
Now,

50:18.415 --> 50:22.019
it's time for me to help my friend
recover his dream.

50:24.321 --> 50:26.656
I'm going to give up my turn for my friend

50:27.924 --> 50:31.528
who helped me find my dream,

50:31.895 --> 50:33.296
and for another friend

50:34.164 --> 50:37.501
who probably cares more about him

50:39.302 --> 50:41.071
than I do.

50:46.943 --> 50:47.844
What?

50:48.478 --> 50:49.913
She's not going to sing?

51:13.637 --> 51:14.938
Thank you.

51:15.372 --> 51:18.341
We have a special performance
in store for you now.

51:19.109 --> 51:20.977
Top star, JB, is here today

51:21.044 --> 51:25.715
to perform a song himself
to give you hope and strength.

51:25.982 --> 51:27.451
A big round of applause, please.

51:44.000 --> 51:46.570
The song I'm about
to perform is "Together."

51:47.104 --> 51:50.574
It was supposed to be a duet,
but my partner couldn't make it.

51:51.508 --> 51:54.044
I'll do my best to do her part as well.

52:04.254 --> 52:05.088
FOR JB &amp; RIAN

52:11.228 --> 52:13.930
