54:54.557 --> 54:57.894
CONCERT FOR PATIENTS

55:29.159 --> 55:30.794
Isn't Hae-seong going to sing?

55:32.095 --> 55:33.963
Hae-seong's a songwriter.

55:41.538 --> 55:42.439
Hang on.

55:43.373 --> 55:44.774
So this means Hae-seong...

55:45.108 --> 55:48.011
She gave up her spot
in the audition for JB.

55:48.478 --> 55:49.546
My goodness.

55:51.514 --> 55:53.683
It's no fun if everything
goes as expected.

55:54.984 --> 55:57.120
Wait, you knew from the start?

55:57.320 --> 55:59.055
It's more fun because I didn't.

56:00.290 --> 56:02.492
What does that mean? Good grief.

56:06.896 --> 56:08.398
What will you get out of this?

56:11.000 --> 56:14.637
I don't make calculations
the same way you do.

56:16.373 --> 56:18.041
I'm not doing this to get something.

56:19.275 --> 56:21.611
I just want to give back
what was given to me.

56:25.281 --> 56:27.417
Are you giving up your spot
in the audition

56:29.119 --> 56:30.754
for JB?

56:32.756 --> 56:33.590
Yes.

56:42.665 --> 56:43.933
Why are you looking at me like that?

56:45.168 --> 56:46.336
You and I...

56:48.104 --> 56:49.773
I guess it's fate.

56:51.141 --> 56:51.975
What?

56:53.176 --> 56:55.578
You got to sing the first one,

56:56.980 --> 56:58.681
and now, the second one.

57:00.183 --> 57:01.251
What do you mean?

57:02.585 --> 57:03.453
I'll look forward to it.

57:25.175 --> 57:27.644
FOR JB &amp; RIAN

57:34.551 --> 57:35.652
I'm asking you a favor.

57:37.253 --> 57:40.690
Please sing this with JB.

57:41.925 --> 57:43.326
But JB was eliminated.

57:44.194 --> 57:45.128
How can he sing this?

57:46.262 --> 57:47.397
I told you

57:48.665 --> 57:51.367
that I would protect JB.

57:54.871 --> 57:57.674
CONCERT FOR PATIENTS

58:00.276 --> 58:01.811
You haven't called me once.

58:02.378 --> 58:03.813
Now you're asking me to do a duet?

58:04.681 --> 58:05.882
Here, of all places?

58:06.950 --> 58:07.784
Yes.

58:20.697 --> 58:21.731
I won't do it for free.

58:23.633 --> 58:25.134
I'm a celebrity.

58:29.272 --> 58:31.207
If I sing this,

58:32.675 --> 58:36.012
treat me to many meals, share with me
the apples your dad sends you,

58:36.579 --> 58:37.881
and do as I say, okay?

58:50.026 --> 58:50.994
Okay.

58:51.794 --> 58:52.762
I'll sing it.

58:54.397 --> 58:56.566
So don't cry.

58:57.467 --> 58:58.301
