59:38.908 --> 59:39.842
so...

59:40.877 --> 59:42.812
Why are you laughing?

59:43.980 --> 59:45.882
Hey, have you talked to her?

59:46.449 --> 59:47.784
Like it would make any different.

59:49.619 --> 59:51.054
