1:00:59.489 --> 1:01:00.790
Did you have fun?

1:01:16.572 --> 1:01:17.674
Oh, dear.

1:01:25.114 --> 1:01:26.449
Why are you laughing?

1:01:29.686 --> 1:01:31.087
Come on!
